{
  "stem": "21437.9",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was just around the corner, or in your own house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And people were talking in the morning-- who was born, who died, you know-- about business or lack of business, whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And this is-- this is why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And did your religious beliefs change from-- because you said before the war, you were Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And did that change?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it slowly, like most of us-- I mean, I was not-- after we-- after the work was done, I mean, I had to work on a Saturday, when we had the milk bar.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I always felt very guilty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I did something on the Shabbat, I always felt very guilty.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if I had to, I did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you know, we all-- after the war, we are not-- people like myself-- we are trying to find sort of little excuses, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK, you know, this is-- we are not so strict.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After all, you are not Ultra-Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I try to-- if I do something on a Shabbat, I still sort of feel like, you know, a twinge.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can literally sort of-- it hurts, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I still feel like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I buy kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, I do sort of-- but I can't say that I really keep, the way my parents kept, and my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wouldn't even, you know-- I wouldn't even compare myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I think that most of the time, I have a clear conscience.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I think that Judaism, is above-- it's got other meanings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't think I'm 100%.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I pick up the phone on a Saturday, if it rings, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I sort of-- things like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So some people, who are really orthodox, they don't, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
